Package: NWQS
Title: Non-Linear Weighted Quantile Sum Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Zhehao", "Wang", , "wangzhehao_bill@foxmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits non-linear weighted quantile sum (NWQS) regression models
    for assessing the joint effect and relative importance of correlated
    mixture exposures. Extends classical WQS by incorporating natural cubic
    splines to capture non-linear dose-response relationships (e.g.,
    threshold, U-shaped, S-shaped curves). Supports Gaussian, binomial,
    Poisson, quasi-Poisson, and conditional logistic regression families.
    Provides repeated holdout estimation, external bootstrap inference,
    permutation-based variable importance, and publication-quality
    diagnostic plots.
